Japanese Pork Belly with Miso Glaze

$25.99
650 kcal

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

PaleoHigh Protein

Tags:

JapanesePorkGlazedComfort Food

Description

Tender pork belly glazed with a savory miso sauce, served with a side of steamed bok choy and rice.

Ingredients

  • Pork belly: 2 lbs
  • Miso paste: 1/2 cup
  • Brown sugar: 1/4 cup
  • Soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • Rice vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • Sesame oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Green onions: 2, chopped
  • Bok choy: 2 heads
  • Jasmine rice: 2 cups
